><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Euthd.\">Euthd.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">297b</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τίνος ἐνδέομεν μὴ οὐ πανσυδίᾳ χωρεῖν</foreign>; <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0006.tlg011.perseus-grc1:797\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ E.\">E.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Tr.\">Tr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">797</biblScope> </bibl> (anap.); after <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὥστε</foreign>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:8:57\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">8.57</biblScope> </bibl>: with the Art., <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">οὐκ ἐναντιώσομαι τὸ μὴ οὐ γεγωνεῖν πᾶν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg003.perseus-grc1:787\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.\">A.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pr.\">Pr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">787</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg003.perseus-grc1:918\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">918</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg004.perseus-grc1:283\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ S.\">S.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ OT\">OT</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">283</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0006.tlg015.perseus-grc1:1176\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ E.\">E.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a c