.\">X.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ HG\">HG</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.2.36</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n67504.9\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> less freq. c. <mood opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"mood\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ part.\">part.</a></mood> after a neg. expressed or implied, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">οὔκων δίκαιον [ἀνδριάντα] ἱστάναι . . μὴ οὐκ ὑπερβαλλόμενον τοῖσι ἔργοισι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:2:110\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.110</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:6:9\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.9</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:106\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">106</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">δυσάλγητος γὰρ ἂν εἴην τοιάνδε μὴ οὐ κατοικτείρων ἕδραν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg004.perseus-grc1:13\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ S.\">S.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ OT\">OT</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">13</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg004.perseus-grc1:221\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">221</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg007.perseus-grc1:360\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ OC\">OC</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">360</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0010.tlg009.perseus-grc1:47\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">